    <item>
      <title>格雷厄姆·普拉特纳在短信丑闻中会见参议院民主党人</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/platner-senate-democrats-washington-meeting.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普拉特纳可能是缅因州参议员的民主党候选人，他在华盛顿会见了几位参议员。少数党领袖查克·舒默回避了有关他对普拉特纳信心的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/platner-senate-democrats-washington-meeting.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 01:53:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州高级选举官员将在大选前几个月辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/texas-top-election-official-resigns.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州州务卿简·尼尔森 (Jane Nelson) 被州长格雷格·阿博特 (Greg Abbott) 任命为监督 2023 年全州选举的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/texas-top-election-official-resigns.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 01:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保护特朗普家族免受国税局侵害的命令布兰奇表示，审计将继续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/trump-irs-settlement.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理总检察长表示，尽管放弃了 18 亿美元的支付基金，但政府仍在保留一项广泛的命令，保护总统及其家人免受对已提交申报表的审计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/trump-irs-settlement.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 00:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
